<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRODERICK MURDERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Betty Broderick is a pathetic, vindictive and psychotic ex-wife who deserves to 
be prosecuted to the full extent of the law, including the death penalty. 
</P>
<P>
Not a soul should shed a tear for this cold-blooded and deranged killer. The 
only sympathy I feel is for her badgered and verbally abused children, who bore 
the brunt of her tantrums over the years. 
</P>
<P>
Dan and Linda Broderick were never allowed to begin their new life together. 
And Betty stands to pay the price. 
</P>
<P>
BRIAN J. BANCROFT 
</P>
<P>
San Clemente 
</P>
