Community. She has lived there with her daughter and four grandchildren since 
June. ; Photo, Dan Stout and his wife, Dennie, plan to be in their own 
apartment soon, along with their two daughters, Sarah, 4, and Amanda, 20 
months. ; Photo, Joseph Walker spruces up a bike donated to the Gateway Family 
Community as Don Goodin, behind, and Hattie Long, left, watch. DAVID McNEW / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
