<DOCID> 250642 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 22, 1990, Sunday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 4; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
695 words 
</P>
