<P>
Guides and brochures on discount shopping are available at no cost. 
</P>
<P>
For brochures on Milford and Norwalk Malls and other outlets, contact 
Connecticut's Tourism Department, Department of Economic Development, 865 Brook 
St., Rocky Hill, Conn. 06067, (203) 258-4290. 
