Freeport, Me. 04032, (207) 865-1212. 
</P>
<P>
The Massachusetts Office of Travel &amp; Tourism, 100 Cambridge St., 13th 
Floor, Boston, Mass. 02202, (617) 727-3493), offers various brochures and a 
listing of factory outlet locations. 
</P>
<P>
For "Vermont Factory Outlets," contact the Vermont Chamber of Commerce, 
Department of Travel and Tourism, Box 37, Montpelier, Vt. 05601, (802) 
223-3443. Jennifer Merin 
</P>
