DESIGNERS; THEATER; ARTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072290-0194 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 251002 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 22, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
